perfsonar-lsregistrationdaemon (3.5.1~3.rc1-5) UNRLEASED; urgency=low

  * Port to Jessie.
  * Adding systemd support.
  * Remove VERBOSE checks from init script.
  * Adding build dependencies for unit tests.
  * Adding dependency to libsys-meminfo-perl.
  * Adding dependencies to new libperfsonar libraries.
  * Not using dh_auto_install but a simpler dh_install.
  * Removing debian/patches that are integrated upstream.
  * Include libraries in package build.

